node version: v4.2.6

Download chromedriver: http://chromedriver.storage.googleapis.com/index.html?path=2.21/ and unzip and put in PATH

Set the following Environment Variables in Travis CI

* SAUCE_USERNAME 
* SAUCE_ACCESS_KEY 

npm install -g grunt-cli
npm install -g webdriverio
npm install -g selenium-standalone@latest
npm install -g jasmine

npm install

try local testing with standalone selenium server: grunt test:local (npm test or grunt)
try multiple browsers testing with SauceLabs: grunt test:saucelab

